originalText.text: The services of Braandy Media have provided a fresh dynamic to my team's arsenal of marketing and advertising content. originalText.text: Jake and Braandy Media has helped represent and put our New York City townhouse on the map. We are a $30 million luxury property located at 80 Washinton Place in the heart of Greenwich Village. Jake has used the new era of online marketing to sling shot our event space forward and bring new angles that we would have never thought of. In a city of “old school” real estate marketing traditions Jake has brought a new meaning to marketing our property the Sousa House. I would highly recommend Braandy Media to any business that’s looking to professionally brand their company on social media or create an online presence.

originalText.text: On behalf of the Florida Hospital Carrollwood Foundation, Jake and his team did an amazing job producing a video for us to use as a important resource to create awareness for the Breast Wellness Centre we are working towards building.  The quality of the video exceeded our expectations and working directly with Jake was a pleasure.  His knowledge and expertise are unparalleled in the industry.  I would recommend Braandy Media to anyone with a need to increase their social media exposure.
